<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rajdeep Das Portfolio</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #141e30, #243b55);
            color: #ddd;
        }

        h1, h2, h3, h4, p {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        a {
            color: #00d9ff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: #1f9ae0;
        }

        /* Header Section */
        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1f2937, #111827);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        header img {
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            box-shadow: 0px 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #00d9ff;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #ddd;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        /* About Section */
        #about {
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        #about h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #00d9ff;
        }

        #about hr {
            width: 150px;
            margin: 10px auto;
            border: 1px solid #00d9ff;
        }

        .skills {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .skills div {
            background: #1f2937;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .skills div h4 {
            color: #00d9ff;
        }

        /* Pricing Section */
        .pricing {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        .pricing-card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1e293b, #17202b);
            padding: 30px;
            width: 250px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .pricing-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .pricing-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #00d9ff;
        }

        .pricing-card ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .pricing-card ul li {
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #444;
        }

        .pricing-card button {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #00d9ff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            color: #000;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .pricing-card button:hover {
            background: #1f9ae0;
        }

        /* Testimonials Section */
        #testimonials {
            padding: 60px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        #testimonials h2 {
            color: #00d9ff;
        }

        .testimonial {
            margin: 20px auto;
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #1f2937;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            position: relative;
        }

        .testimonial:before {
            content: "“";
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #00d9ff;
            position: absolute;
            top: -20px;
            left: 20px;
        }

        .testimonial:after {
            content: "”";
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #00d9ff;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -20px;
            right: 20px;
        }

        .testimonial p {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #ddd;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background: #111827;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            color: #ddd;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #00d9ff;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200" alt="Rajdeep Das">
        <h1>Rajdeep Das</h1>
        <p>Innovator in Tech | Founder of BongBeast Infotech Pvt. Ltd.</p>
    </header>

    <!-- About -->
    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <hr>
        <p>I am Rajdeep Das, a passionate B.Tech student in Computer Science and Engineering, committed to creating transformative tech solutions.</p>

        <div class="skills">
            <div>
                <h4>Full Stack Development</h4>
                <p>Proficient in modern frameworks.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4>Cloud Computing</h4>
                <p>Expertise in scalable solutions.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing -->
    <section class="pricing">
        <div class="pricing-card">
            <h3>Basic</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Front-End Development</li>
                <li>UX/UI Design</li>
            </ul>
            <button>Sign Up</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>© 2024 Rajdeep Das | Built with ❤ in Kolkata</p>
    </footer>

</body>

</html>
